  "text": "Gender and level of education did not influence CI speech performance of postlinguistically deaf adults. The inclusion criteria of the present study paid particular attention to distinguish level of education and language acquisition. The age at beginning of s/p HL had to be later than 15 years old, in order to avoid bias related to potentially delayed development of speech processing in severely deaf children [CITATION_1] .",
